data.description: BACKYARD OASIS! Charming 2-story tastefully updated home on quiet cul-de-sac street in master planned Fairfield! Walk to elementary school. Stunning entry w/curved wrought iron staircase! Gorgeous hardwood floors flow into private study w/French doors, formal dining, into the 2-story family room, breakfast area & kitchen! Large family room features custom built-ins & gas fireplace! Large kitchen w/contrasting color island, 42" cabinets, granite counters & stainless appliances including gas cooktop! Whole home water softener. Breakfast room w/custom built-in desk. Master bedroom w/spa-like en-suite including oversized frameless shower & California closet. Upstairs boasts a gameroom, 6x5 data center, 3 spacious secondary bedrooms & 2 baths (1 full/1 jack-n-jill). Fabulous backyard oasis complete w/2 covered patios, outdoor grill station, sparkling pool w/beach entry, sun deck w/diving pad, spa & rock waterfall! Full sprinkler system & French drains. CFISD! Walking distance to Keith Elem.
